<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>学年解散飲み会 招待状</title>
<!-- ✅ 修正: 2つのフォントを別々の<link>に分割 -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Zen+Maru+Gothic:wght@400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=M+PLUS+Rounded+1c:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe0f0 0%, #ffd6f0 25%, #e8d6ff 50%, #d6eeff 75%, #d6ffe8 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 32px 16px;
    font-family: 'Zen Maru Gothic', sans-serif;
  }

  .confetti {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .dot {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: float linear infinite;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0% { transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg); opacity: 0; }
    10% { opacity: 0.5; }
    90% { opacity: 0.5; }
    100% { transform: translateY(-100px) rotate(720deg); opacity: 0; }
  }

  .card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-radius: 32px;
    max-width: 520px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 48px 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(200, 150, 200, 0.25), 0 0 0 1.5px rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .deco-top {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 36px;
    letter-spacing: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9ec8, #d89fff);
    color: white;
    font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    padding: 5px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .title {
    font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 30px;
    color: #c060a0;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #b090c0;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .divider {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .divider-line {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #f0c0e0, transparent);
  }

  .divider-star {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #f0a0d0;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 14px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,220,240,0.4), rgba(230,210,255,0.4));
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,200,230,0.5);
  }

  .info-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(200,150,200,0.15);
  }

  .info-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #cc88bb;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }

  .info-value {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #7050a0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .info-sub {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: #a080c0;
    margin-top: 3px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .notice-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff5d0, #ffe8f0);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 14px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid #ffd0a0;
    margin-top: 14px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .notice-box .info-icon {
    background: white;
  }

  .notice-text {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: #a06020;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .notice-text strong {
    color: #d04040;
  }

  .rsvp-section {
    margin-top: 28px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .rsvp-deadline {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #c060a0;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .rsvp-deadline span {
    background: #ffe0f0;
    padding: 3px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    color: #d04080;
  }

  .rsvp-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff8fc0, #bf8fff);
    color: white;
    font-family: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 16px;
    padding: 16px 48px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(200,100,200,0.35), 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .rsvp-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.03);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(200,100,200,0.4), 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  }

  .rsvp-btn:active {
    transform: translateY(0) scale(0.99);
  }

  .footer-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #c0a0d0;
    margin-top: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .deco-bottom {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -2px; left: -2px; right: -2px; bottom: -2px;
    border-radius: 34px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffb0d8, #e0a0ff, #a0d0ff, #a0ffcc);
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .card { padding: 36px 24px; }
    .title { font-size: 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="confetti" id="confetti"></div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="deco-top">🥂 🌸 🍻</div>

  <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:20px;">
    <div class="tag">✨ INVITATION ✨</div>
    <div class="title">学年解散飲み会<br>のご案内</div>
    <div class="subtitle">みんなで楽しく締めくくろう！</div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <div class="divider-star">🌷</div>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="info-grid">

    <div class="info-item">
      <div class="info-icon">📅</div>
      <div>
        <div class="info-label">DATE &amp; TIME</div>
        <div class="info-value">3月19日（木）18:00 〜 20:00</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-item">
      <div class="info-icon">📍</div>
      <div>
        <div class="info-label">VENUE</div>
        <div class="info-value">新時代</div>
        <div class="info-sub">水戸市城南1丁目4-12 柏木ビル1階<br>駅南中央通りをまっすぐ → パチンコ屋を過ぎ →<br>香陵住販（不動産屋）の角を曲がるとすぐ！</div>
        <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJ68IrcAAlImARAWymxHF-dG8" target="_blank" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;margin-top:8px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:#e05090;background:rgba(255,200,230,0.35);border:1.5px solid rgba(220,130,180,0.4);border-radius:100px;padding:4px 12px;text-decoration:none;">📍 Google マップで見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-item">
      <div class="info-icon">💰</div>
      <div>
        <div class="info-label">FEE</div>
        <div class="info-value">3,850円</div>
        <div class="info-sub">2時間飲み放題コース 🍺<br>おつりあり・お札大歓迎！お気軽にどうぞ 😊<br>PayPayでのお支払いも受け付けています！<br>わからないことがあれば小林まで！</div>
        <a href="https://qr.paypay.ne.jp/p2p01_rhmur2kmEa0IseaV" target="_blank" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;margin-top:8px;font-size:11.5px;font-weight:700;color:#d04090;background:rgba(255,200,230,0.35);border:1.5px solid rgba(220,130,180,0.4);border-radius:100px;padding:4px 12px;text-decoration:none;">💸 PayPayで送金する（幹事：小林）</a>

      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="info-item">
      <div class="info-icon">👗</div>
      <div>
        <div class="info-label">DRESS CODE</div>
        <div class="info-value">カジュアルな服装で OK！</div>
        <div class="info-sub">串焼き居酒屋のため、煙のにおいがつく可能性があります。<br>ラフなお召し物がおすすめです。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="notice-box">
    <div class="info-icon" style="font-size:18px;">ℹ️</div>
    <div class="notice-text">
      大衆居酒屋のため個室ではありません。すみません。席の間隔も狭めなことご了承ください。
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider" style="margin:24px 0 20px;">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <div class="divider-star">🎀</div>
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="rsvp-section">
    <div class="rsvp-deadline">🍾 <span>二次会意欲調査</span></div>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#b080c0;margin:8px 0 16px;line-height:1.6;">参考にしたいので必ず二次会があるわけではありません！<br>気軽に答えてください！</p>
    <a href="https://forms.gle/jJHHmZYFWoX8GHuK8" class="rsvp-btn" target="_blank">
      🌟 二次会アンケートはこちら 🌟
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-note">
    ぜひ楽しい会にしましょう✨
  </div>

  <div class="deco-bottom">🌸 🎉 🌸</div>
</div>

<script>
const colors = ['#ffb0d0','#d0a0ff','#a0d0ff','#ffe0a0','#a0ffcc','#ffcca0'];
const confetti = document.getElementById('confetti');
for (let i = 0; i < 40; i++) {
  const dot = document.createElement('div');
  dot.className = 'dot';
  const size = Math.random() * 10 + 4;
  dot.style.cssText = `
    width:${size}px;height:${size}px;
    background:${colors[Math.floor(Math.random()*colors.length)]};
    left:${Math.random()*100}%;
    animation-duration:${Math.random()*12+8}s;
    animation-delay:${Math.random()*10}s;
  `;
  confetti.appendChild(dot);
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
